# G middleware

Wrap an existing route's handler with a chi middleware. Idempotent.

1. Ask the user for `<METHOD> <path> <middleware-ref>` (e.g.
   `POST /orders/{id}/archive auth.RequireRole("admin")`).
2. Run `gofasta g middleware <args> --dry-run --json` to preview.
3. If the generator reports `ROUTE_ALREADY_WRAPPED`, the middleware
   is already applied — confirm with the user before re-running.
4. Otherwise re-run without `--dry-run` to apply.
